    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, BaseContingency, DepContingency, DepIEquivOutageBranch, DepIOutageIslanding, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class DepContingencyImpl
extends BaseContingencyImpl
implements DepContingency
    An implementation of the model object 'Contingency'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Total Islands
    • Max Shifted Flow
    • Max Shift Flow Branch Id
    • Outage Branches
    • Island Buses
    • Equiv Outage Branches
